Actors cast
-----------

Choose python version::

  $   if [ -z "$PYTHON" ]; then
  >      PYTHON="python"
  >   fi

Add opster to the PYTHONPATH::

  $   if [ -z "$OPSTER_DIR" ]; then
  >      OPSTER_DIR="$TESTDIR/.."
  >   fi
  >   export PYTHONPATH="$OPSTER_DIR"

Define function to make it simpler::

  $ run() {
  >   name=$1
  >   shift
